description:
{{toBsonValueList}} casts {{Bson}} objects to {{BsonValue}} which errors when the actual value is eg. a {{Document}}.

{code:java}
MongoCollection<Document> collection = // ...

Document existing = collection.findOneAndUpdate(
    new Document("_id", 1), 
    Collections.singletonList(
        new Document("$set", new Document("title", "The Burning White"))
    ),
    new FindOneAndUpdateOptions().upsert(true));
{code}

When creating a data encryption key via the createKey() method for client-side field level encryption, a new document is created that contains fields such as a UUID, encrypted key, creationDate, updateDate, status, and masterKey document.

 

